---
title: Bacon & Scallop Mushroom Risotto with Parsley & Lemon Wedges
description: Scallops love bacon and the feeling is mutual! And what better way to let this surf-and-turf romance blossom than on a bed of creamy mushroom risotto? Some of the crisped bacon is stirred into the risotto so you’ll get a little bit of smoky goodness in every bite. The sweet scallops served on top are seared and butter-basted so they’re extra luscious. Is it getting hot in here? No, just us?
